    <text x="20" y="350" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13">ADM must file a report for possible referral to Rome prosecutors</text>
    <text x="350" y="415" fill="#52525b" font-size="12" text-anchor="middle">Source: SBC News, Il Sole 24 Ore, OneFootball, CFTC (as of 7/10/2026)</text>
